Collections.rule:
Individual: @P*(mm:Replace("|", " ") mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)
Types: CPU
Facts: part_of @AE*,
  has_cores @Q*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  clock_frequency @P*(["(\d+(?:\.\d)+[ ]?[MG]Hz)"])

Individual:  @S*(mm:Replace("|", " ") mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)
Types: GPU
Facts: part_of @AE*

Individual: @AE*
Types: model
Annotations: price_eur @AC*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  image @AD*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  rdfs:label @B*
Facts: made_by @A*,
  supports @C*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  supports @D*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  supports @E*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  supports @F*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  announced @G*(["(\d+)"] mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  dimensions @H*(["(\d+(?:\.\d+)? x \d+(?:\.\d+)? x \d+(?:\.\d+)?)"] mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  weight @I*(["(\d+(?:\.\d+)?)"] mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  supports @J*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  display_size @L*(["(\d+(?:\.\d+)?)"] mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  display_resolution  @M*(["(\d+ x \d+) pixels"] mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  has_os @N*(mm:Replace("|", " ") mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  supports @T*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  has_memory @U*(["(\d+(?:\.\d+)?) GB"] mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  has_ram @V*(["(\d+(?:\.\d+)?) GB"] mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  primary_camera  @W*(["(\d+(?:\.\d+)?)"] mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  secondary_camera  @X*(["(\d+(?:\.\d+)?)"] mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  supports @Y*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  supports @Z*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  supports @AA*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
  battery @AB* (["((?:Li-Po)|(?:Li-Ion)|(?:Ni-Mh))"]  mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)

Individual:  @R*(mm:Replace("|", " ") mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)
Types: Chipset
Facts: part_of @AE*
